                                <expan>Weynsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> mit dem edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                                <expan>Weinsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, zu reden etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auf <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> zeit
                        auch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gen <expan>Heylprunn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        guten <expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> des reichs stetten und auch
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
